(20, 36, 'Bao son Hotel', 'bao-son-hotel', 'Nguyen Chi Thanh Ha Noi', '', '0', '', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Just 4 miles from Diamond Head Crater Park, this central Waikiki luxury resort features an oceanfront pool with a 70-foot water slide. A full-service spa and free Wi-Fi are offered.Modern rooms feature a flat-screen TV and video games at Sheraton Waikiki. Rooms are simply styled and offer a private balcony, some with mountain or ocean views. In-room coffee and a work desk are also provided.The Sheraton offers 4 on-site dining options, including tapas restaurant Rum Fire. Other choices include a fresh food market and a sushi bar.A tour desk and child care services are offered at this resort. Fitness and business facilities are also located on-site for guest convenience.Honolulu Zoo and Kapiolani Park are 2 miles from the resort. Waikiki Shopping Centre is just a 6-minute walk away</p>', '<p><span style="text-align: justify;">Just 4 miles from Diamond Head Crater Park, this central Waikiki luxury resort features an oceanfront pool with a 70-foot water slide. A full-service spa and free Wi-Fi are offered.Modern rooms feature a flat-screen TV and video games at Sheraton Waikiki. Rooms are simply styled and offer a private balcony, some with mountain or ocean views. In-room coffee and a work desk are also provided.The Sheraton offers 4 on-site dining options, including tapas restaurant Rum Fire. Other choices include a fresh food market and a sushi bar.A tour desk and child care services are offered at this resort. Fitness and business facilities are also located on-site for guest convenience.Honolulu Zoo and Kapiolani Park are 2 miles from the resort. Waikiki Shopping Centre is just a 6-minute walk away</span></p>', 4, 2147483647, 0, 1, 'quan@ibookingonline.com', '', '\\oc-combi-5.jpg', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0),
