nerary</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px 2px 5px; border: 0px; background-image: url(''http://www.footstepsinstyle.com/wp-content/themes/linguini/images/point-content.png''); background-position: 10px 10px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">Tours, transfers and all services as mentioned in the itinerary</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px 2px 5px; border: 0px; background-image: url(''http://www.footstepsinstyle.com/wp-content/themes/linguini/images/point-content.png''); background-position: 10px 10px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">Services of a driver and air-conditioned vehicles during all transfers</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px 2px 5px; border: 0px; background-image: url(''http://www.footstepsinstyle.com/wp-content/themes/linguini/images/point-content.png''); background-position: 10px 10px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">Entrance fees for all sights visited</li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px 2px 5px; border: 0px; background-image: url(''http://www.footstepsinstyle.com/wp-content/themes/linguini/images/point-content.png''); background-position: 10px 10px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">Boat trips as mentioned in the itinerary</li>\r\n</ul>', '2013-11-12', '2013-09-26', '', '', '', '9:00', 17, '1-3;4-6;7-12', 'shared', 16, 0);
